      'Lead discovery, architecture, & development of continuous Dark Web monitoring product',
    ],
  },
  {
    date: 'July 2022 - April 2023',
    company: 'Coalfire',
    title: 'Senior Full-Stack Software Engineer',
    details: [
      'Drive architecture & development of an application to automate cybersecurity gap assessments and generate client deliverables',
      'Lead architecture & development of the worldâ€™s first automated OSCAL submission desktop application to secure a $16 million DoD contract',
      'Drive implementation of new product development processes to streamline the SDLC between stakeholders and developers',
    ],
  },
  {
    date: 'September 2021 - July 2022',
    company: 'Frontpoint Security',
    title: 'Senior Software Engineer',
    details: [
      'Lead development of engineering support software such as legal PDF reporting for GDPR and legal subpoena requests with Python & Go',
